raw_mentions:
2-((3-(4-cyanonaphthalen-l-yl)pyridin-4-yl)thio)-2-methylpropanoic acid has an EC50 value < 0.05 μΜ. 
2-((3-(4-cyanonaphthalen-l-yl)pyridin-4-yl)thio)-2-methylpropanoic acid or vehicle is added in assay buffer with <sup>14</sup>C-uric acid for a final concentration of 125μΜ Uric Acid with a specific activity of 54 mCi/mmol.
